{"tid":1667104,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴刺客認罪還押候判 控方指相信是全球首類巴士放針案件","createTime":"2019-10-21T09:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T09:49:43.000Z","uid":7439,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"08865b6e429119cc2fc523fcf59057bc82ea8071","tid":1667104,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3434614/org/4d5e20584965772e1b9ab063d9a6971c.jpg/RdUnkdHbyZYIy5yyJxRWTyE0l77RoINPcJ_ncnCf53I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3434614%2Forg%2F4d5e20584965772e1b9ab063d9a6971c.jpg%2FRdUnkdHbyZYIy5yyJxRWTyE0l77RoINPcJ_ncnCf53I&h=f2fc3a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多架九巴的座椅去年年中驚現插針，數名乘客因而被刺傷，警方事後拘捕涉在其中2輛巴士插針的無業漢。該男子今（21日）於區域法院承認兩項有意圖而企圖傷人罪，及兩項刑事毀壞罪，他被捕後曾供稱：「啲巴士成日飛站，咁我咪落針拮啲乘客。」法官決定先為他索取背景、精神及心理報告，將判刑押後至下月12日，其間被告繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n被告莫湛深，31歲，與事主並不相識。他承認於去年6月27日，分別在一輛41A線及一輛48X線的九巴座位放置縫紉針，意圖使任何坐在該上層座位的人身體受嚴重傷害，而企圖非法及惡意傷害該人；以及無合理辯解下損毀上述座位。<br />\n<br />\n三名乘客先後被刺傷<br />\n案情指，當晚6時半，一名女乘客在尖沙咀登上41A 巴士上層，坐於後幾排窗邊位時，左臀突被尖物刺到，赫然發現座位中央竟垂直插著一根尖端朝上、長約4厘米的縫紉針。她通知車長後再報警，並將針交予警方。<br />\n<br />\n另外兩名被刺的女乘客則於7時在沙田登上48X號巴士。其中一人坐於上層較後位置時大腿被刺，轉換座位後發現縫紉針；她見到另一人隨即坐在涉案座椅，但似乎若無其事，故未有提醒。後來該名乘客感到有異，換位後見到插針，再告知九巴及警方。三名被刺乘客均有到醫院檢查，幸無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n被告乘車途中數次換位<br />\n警方調查發現，被告當日下午4時至8時乘搭過4輛巴士。閉路電視顯示，被告登上涉案車輛後，在插針位旁邊有所動作，下車前又數次換位。有其他乘客作供指，於較早前曾坐在涉案位置，但不覺有異；而在他們下車至有人被刺的期間，只有被告一人坐於涉案座椅的旁邊。<br />\n<br />\n被告家中檢獲7根縫紉針<br />\n被告事後一周在寓所被捕，警誡下道：「啲巴士成日飛站，咁我咪落針拮啲乘客。」警方在屋內搜出他案發時所穿衣物，並在其家中檢獲7根縫紉針。<br />\n<br />\n被告過往並無案底，辯方表示他早前上庭沒有即時認罪，但其後改變想法，望法庭可扣減4分1刑罰。控方稱，事主未有向被告索償，但有人就事件入稟控告九巴。被告自被捕開始還押，但巴士插針事件仍有發生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3434631/org/b93e10d93ca54d98db611a2bfae1dbe5.jpg/QMkXH-stqugS11mPcsZdGfmtaGtFT9ZkkvMjIZLzIyE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3434631%2Forg%2Fb93e10d93ca54d98db611a2bfae1dbe5.jpg%2FQMkXH-stqugS11mPcsZdGfmtaGtFT9ZkkvMjIZLzIyE&h=3d96aa9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a525a59a71dcad5b9c9cafab03eb3c6707e96e00","tid":1667104,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:30:25.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a949ba3c6f073d44fc8af20c7773350d6be85f","tid":1667104,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"控方指被告初犯，沒有案底。法官希望先為被告索取背景報告、精神科報告及心理報告再考慮判刑。控方又透露，本案受害人正向巴士公司進行民事索償，而巴士公司則未有向被告進行追討。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>控方欲向法官呈上判刑指引時指，在本地及普通法國家中沒有類似案件，相信為全球首宗如此犯案的案件。</strong></span>法官將案件押後至11月12日，先替被告索取精神及心理報告，期間還押侯判。"},{"pid":"04522b3013caa7fbf698ceb733582e89dcb06542","tid":1667104,"uid":7439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"案情指，被告於2018年6月27日下午4時至7時許，乘搭41A、81、48X及49X巴士，由青衣長安巴士總站乘搭至尖沙咀、沙田禾輋、沙田新城市廣場等地，再折返原地，<span style=\"color: red;\">全程均使用現金支付。</span><br />\n<br />\n41A 青衣&gt;油尖旺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n81 油尖旺&gt;禾輋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n48X 禾輋&gt;新城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n49X 新城市&gt;青衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc27f77aa33e923275e4b50de517ea4b964d8b1","tid":1667104,"uid":124277,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:33:47.000Z","msg":"全球首宗, 人生無白過<br />\n好感概我到底做緊乜"},{"pid":"627c6a62e6abddbc5d508c3e693eb2e6a297af18","tid":1667104,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a9b6020a789e14a0e624e628ca48ca30ee0b80","tid":1667104,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:34:44.000Z","msg":"圖右<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/10/20191021_CR_%E8%8E%AB%E6%B9%9B%E6%B7%B12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F10%2F20191021_CR_%25E8%258E%25AB%25E6%25B9%259B%25E6%25B7%25B12.jpg&h=6367142a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82be5fc84557c79964d59cf85a38d751d403b544","tid":1667104,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:35:56.000Z","msg":"第28庭 9字樓 Court No.28(9/F)<br />\n姚勳智法官 H.H. Judge Yiu<br />\n<br />\n上午09:30 am 法庭聆訊 Open Court<br />\n <br />\n刑事案件<br />\nDCCC 80/2019<br />\n<br />\nHKSAR (香港特別行政區) v.MOK CHAM SUM (莫湛深)<br />\n<br />\n聆取對控罪的回答Plea<br />\n<br />\n律政司 Department of Justice<br />\n任其昌李鴻生律師行 Johnnie Yam, Jacky Lee &amp; Co.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情人節提堂郭偉健<br />\n而家變咗姚勳智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab91f4eb4c94e17fe7ffd9c3c4d9aae06de9b6e1","tid":1667104,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nume.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/WhatsApp-Image-2019-09-26-at-12.54.34-PM.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnume.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2019-09-26-at-12.54.34-PM.jpeg&h=236d8e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3434630/org/9229cc535f192dd790b286092195bc16.jpg/ZccHPxY94FJV6hnZACYyTzxmI4UWdkyuF-Q5XRfkOV0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3434630%2Forg%2F9229cc535f192dd790b286092195bc16.jpg%2FZccHPxY94FJV6hnZACYyTzxmI4UWdkyuF-Q5XRfkOV0&h=fdc3a13a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n345被告做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0236d182f31cbd2b6a12351bc90460916cda1801","tid":1667104,"uid":263186,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"重判啦 呢啲仆街"},{"pid":"851f0c418a4804cbcdca96304a18b160db430a25","tid":1667104,"uid":49891,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:47:11.000Z","msg":"@N賓"},{"pid":"fb7a164a898a59e876550d17d7c8e3e954e8aaf7","tid":1667104,"uid":35348,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:47:12.000Z","msg":"呢個係替死鬼 真兇仲係波台9up緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe5dfd27005cacc123d0601b73ab95fca8dd9b6","tid":1667104,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"7e86b105356691d309f9c98e0ff589edad5cf7ce","tid":1667104,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb7a164a898a59e876550d17d7c8e3e954e8aaf7","tid":1667104,"uid":35348,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:47:12.000Z","msg":"呢個係替死鬼 真兇仲係波台9up緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/