sg":"nben仲未入？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"畀人拉咗點入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29339ed360ac5c4a51a543093b64431cf455eb75","tid":1667104,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:25:41.000Z","msg":"我去緊保釋佢"},{"pid":"9612e869149825866e9151eb0e608083c090769f","tid":1667104,"uid":66925,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f04G5ip.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff04G5ip.png&h=61537b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明係休班警做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59410954cd93289208de750a7bd6243cb67a5c03","tid":1667104,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">N Ben</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4062c4a675d2f47baa23901b1804a95be033c04","tid":1667104,"uid":162910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:29:46.000Z","msg":"竟然重有狗做正事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b87bef0085af441ef65e5928ba5c2af6769710","tid":1667104,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:49:01.000Z","msg":"據悉，該名姓莫的男疑犯，於2014年與一名男子合資開設一間數碼用品有限公司，售賣手機相關用品，並於荃灣悅來坊商場地下位置開店。但其後疑因管理不善，該店最終結業收場及解散。而莫更陷入財困，前年7月他被債主申請破產。另外，自疑犯的數碼公司結業後，他終日無所事事當上「隱蔽青年」，性情大變的他更鮮有出門。"},{"pid":"33cd4c56456a02a48d92cdb61693c960118f47a5","tid":1667104,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:51:43.000Z","msg":"案情指出，被告於去年6月27日下午4時47分至7時37分，先在青衣長安巴士總站登上一輛41A九巴巴士，於尖沙嘴聖安德烈教堂下車，其後在油麻地登上一輛81號巴士在沙田禾輋巴士總站下車，再轉乘48X巴士到沙田新城巿廣場，之後登上49X巴士返回青衣長安巴士總站。<br />\n<br />\n一名女乘客在同日晚上約6時半，登上涉案41A巴士上層，一坐下左邊臀部被尖銳物件刺到，立刻感到痛楚跳起來，發現座位中央垂直插着一根縫紉針，尖端向上，她將針拔走放在藥丸膠袋，拍下照片，下車時告知涉案巴士司機，同日再報警及到醫院診治，發現左邊臀部有一處表面刺傷但無流血。<br />\n<br />\n同日晚上7時許，兩名女乘客分別在沙田新城市廣場登上48X巴士，並坐在上層座位上，其中一名女乘客感到左大腿被尖銳物件刺到而換位，隨後另一名女乘客坐在該座位上，同樣感到左大腿被尖銳物件刺到，轉換坐姿時，右大腿又被刺到，始發現座位中央有尖銳物件外露，在荃灣下車時告知一名九巴職員，兩人均到醫院診治。<br />\n<br />\n被告去年7月4日在家中被捕，在警誡下承認「啲巴士成日飛站，咁我咪落針拮啲乘客」，並稱案發當日他打算到佐敦購物，及後改變主意到沙田新城巿廣場。另九巴車上閉路電視曾拍攝到被告在涉案巴士上多次轉換座位的情況。"},{"pid":"7e67e8659ddd93b689664a43ebc5178eaa3357e5","tid":1667104,"uid":202348,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"「啲巴士成日飛站，咁我咪落針拮啲乘客。」<br />\n<br />\n口吻都似N賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bbaf4f265b6cac30d7ebf474a44ebd182fb475","tid":1667104,"uid":8572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"n賓消失了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7541b31b41615063db18485b4935e21d7f69d0","tid":1667104,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"pepe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ccc尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1f24dda45f6981102ccab76ee9f92b0eef4798","tid":1667104,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23bbaf4f265b6cac30d7ebf474a44ebd182fb475","tid":1667104,"uid":8572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"n賓消失了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:31:14.000Z","msg":"喺赤柱畀人拮了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf77a7d45cfc611835babcd1f0fc5ae3377aee7","tid":1667104,"uid":5549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fb7a164a898a59e87